#####################ELASTIC KUBERNETES SERVICE CLUSTER CREATION#########################

1) Create IAM role with "AmazonEKSClusterPolicy" policy for creating kubernetes cluster.

2) Create the kubernetes cluster in the eks dashboard with IAM role that we have created.

3) Create IAM role with 3 policies(AmazonEKSWorkerNodePolicy, AmazonEC2ContainerRegistryReadOnly and AmazonEKS_CNI_Policy) for creating the kubernetes NodeGroup.

4) Open the created cluster and navigate to compute tab and create Node group using the IAM role that we have created.
